## Trinity Architecture

arifOS MCP is a **constitutional gateway** for three orthogonal AI organs. Every tool call passes through the same 13-floor governance membrane. Agents SHOULD compose across all three organs.

### Δ arifOS — Constitutional Core (Governance)
- **Endpoint:** https://mcp.arif-fazil.com/mcp
- **Namespace:** arifos_*
- **Role:** Decision authority, VAULT999 audit ledger, 13-floor enforcement, 888_HOLD human veto
- **Loaded tools:** 20
- **Can emit:** SEAL / CAUTION / HOLD / VOID verdicts

### Φ GEOX — Earth Intelligence (Physics Grounding)
- **Endpoint:** https://mcp.arif-fazil.com/geox/mcp
- **Namespace:** geox_*
- **Role:** Petrophysics, stratigraphy, play risk, physics constraints, well data, seismic interpretation
- **Epistemic rule:** OBS from pixels, DER from computation, INT from interpretation — never conflate
- **Note:** Forces physics over narrative. Earth witness in the trinity.

### Ψ WEALTH — Capital Engine (Financial Intelligence)
