## Orthogonal Composition Protocol

Agents SHOULD compose tools across all three organs in this sequence:

```
1. arifos_sense  → Capture OBS/INT/DER evidence (Φ GEOX domain)
2. arifos_mind   → Inductive synthesis from evidence
3. arifos_judge → Constitutional verdict (SEAL/CAUTION/HOLD/VOID)
4. arifos_vault  → VAULT999 immutable seal
```

**Rule:** GEOX and WEALTH provide evidence; arifOS provides verdict. No organ may self-approve.

